**Metrics to track (per research-integrity.md §6):**

| Metric | Formula | Target |
|--------|---------|--------|
| **Annualized Return** | `(1 + total_return) ^ (252/days) - 1` | > 10% excess |
| **Sharpe Ratio** | `√252 × mean(r) / std(r)` | > 1.0 |
| **Max Drawdown** | `max(peak-to-trough loss)` | < 20% |
| **Turnover** | `mean(daily_holdings_change)` | < 30% monthly |
| **Win Rate** | `% profitable months` | > 55% |
| **Long-Short Return** | `Q5 - Q1 annualized` | > 8% |

